  "body": "### Scope\r\n\r\nTracking performance issues and optimizations that can be implemented to address them.\r\n\r\n### Topics\r\n\r\n- [ ] Slowdown due to DB performance\r\n  - Following on the discussion https://github.com/status-im/status-go/pull/3593#discussion_r1226238241\r\n  - Good questions raised there:\r\n    - what will be the expected dynamic performance of the filter in the worst case scenario\r\n    - what is the worst case scenario and are the performance of index good enough or should we optimize them\r\n- [ ] Provide a way for UX to cancel the current filter API async request in case it is too long. Extend status-go with `filterActivityCancelCurrentAsyncTask`",
